  "texts": [
    "Therefore, we have been motivated to develop a successful probability prediction model for the 6G-SQC project.",
    "To address the study objective, firstly, we explore the potential variables that could impact the success of the 6G-SQC project reported in the literature.",
    "Next, we collected the experts' insights on the identified variables using a survey questionnaire for developing a training dataset.",
    "Finally, we applied the Genetic Algorithm to Naive Bayes Classifier (NBC) and Logistic Regression (LR) to develop the success probability prediction model for 6G-SQC projects by analyzing the data collected from experts.",
    "This model will enable practitioners to assess the success probability of the 6G-SQC project, and we believe these findings will significantly contribute to developing effective strategies for addressing critical aspects of the 6G-SQC project."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}